name: Valentino Rossi Sketch
description:
Valentino Rossi Sketch - By Richard Koscher - https://www.richardkoscherart.com/

The most famous “46” in sports history will retire in 2021. 9x MotoGP Champion Valentino “The Doctor” Rossi. I have seen Vale many times in Laguna Seca, California and the Circuit of the Americas in Austin Texas and have been cheering for him since I can remember.
